short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This tool will help you examine the implementation of AIQUA Web SDK.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This tool will examine if a website is installed AIQUA SDK and list all of the traffic coming out from SDK in order to help you check the correctness of SDK installation.
